June 18, 2016 D Eidgenössisches Musikfest (Unterstufe BB, qualifying Round)
Eidgenössisches Musikfest (Unterstufe BB) 70 Own Choice Test Piece Contest Eidgenössisches Musikfest eidgenossisches-musikfest-unterstufe-bb
Entertainments Contest
Salle de Gymnastique Rambert C Tavel, Montreux, VD, Switzerland Wöflinswil and Obermumpf advanced to 'Cup' - Semifinal, for best Entertainment Bands (not qualified for Final).
Winner of 'Cup' Unterstufe: Regionale Jugendmusik Young Winds Goldach; 22 Bands competed (Wind & 7 Brass Bands).
Winner of 'Cup' Oberstufe [Superior]: Harmoniemusik Kriens; 4 Bands competed (no Brass Bands).
March 3, 2016, 12:24 p.m. May 1, 2018, 2:52 p.m.
